  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Infants/children with cow's milk allergy will take part in 2 double-blinded
      placebo-controlled food challenges (DBPCFC) of 2 extensively hydrolyzed formulas in random
      order. If both food challenges are passed, subjects will be asked to consume the Test formula
      in an at-home open challenge for 7 days.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
